					<img src="http://archive.org/download/rilla_ingleside_librivox/Rilla_of_Ingleside_1007.jpg" alt="book-cover-large" width="175" height="175" />

										<a href="http://archive.org/download/rilla_ingleside_librivox/Rilla_of_Ingleside_1007.jpg" class="download-cover">Download cover art</a>
					
